      "content": "thanks for the list. i've heard Cary is good but i'm also curious about how the vibe changes if i look at more diverse areas like near durham or parts of raleigh. are those districts still considered \"stable\" or \"safe\" for families, or should i stick to the more suburban ones you mentioned?",
